{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"302ea2cf4d","title":"中原军区部队应争取合法转移","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b3f5b27a6c","index":0,"year":1946,"month":4,"day":30,"articleId":"302ea2cf4d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d0312a524f","type":"paragraph","text":"中原军区部队应争取合法转移口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"302ea2cf4d"},{"id":"b80b780c81","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年4月30日）郑、李、王（一）只要顽军不破裂，应依原计争取合法转移为上策。（二）假如顽军破裂向你们大举进攻而迫便你们非突围不可时，你们准备向何方向前进，向西还是向东，二者利害及前途如何，望预先秘密新划并电告。（三）五月上半月必须将二方人复员完毕。（四）王震环要来延”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"302ea2cf4d"},{"id":"6bddffa0c2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"302ea2cf4d"},{"id":"8513128a5d","type":"paragraph","text":"师三十]抗目战争胜利后，国民党调集重兵如紧包围和蚕食以玻交界的宜为中心的中原解放区，全图首先消灭中原军区部队，打通向华东、华练北进军的通道。为此，毛泽东为中共中央越草了这份给中共中央中原攀书记落中原军区政治委员郑位三、司令员李先念和副句令员兼参谋长电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"302ea2cf4d"}],"page":{"id":"c4dc873999","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"302ea2cf4d","start":287,"end":287}}}},"__N_SSG":true}